#: common/dialogs/dialog_autosave_recovery_base.cpp:29
msgid ""
"Replaces your saved file with the auto-saved version. The previous saved "
"content is discarded."
msgstr "ແທນທີ່ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ທ່ານບັນທຶກດ້ວຍເວີຊັນທີ່ບັນທຶກອັດຕະໂນມັດ. ເນື້ອໃນທີ່ບັນທຶກໄວ້ກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້ຈະຖືກຍົກເລີກ."

#: common/dialogs/dialog_autosave_recovery_base.cpp:33
msgid "Keep Current"
msgstr "ຮັກສາເວີຊັນປັດຈຸບັນ"

#: common/dialogs/dialog_autosave_recovery_base.cpp:34
msgid "Keeps your saved file as-is and discards the auto-saved changes."
msgstr "ຮັກສາໄຟລ໌ທີ່ບັນທຶກໄວ້ຄືເກົ່າ ແລະ ຍົກເລີກການປ່ຽນແປງທີ່ບັນທຶກອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#: common/dialogs/dialog_autosave_recovery_base.cpp:38
msgid "Keep Both"
msgstr "ຮັກສາໄວ້ທັງສອງ"

#: common/dialogs/dialog_autosave_recovery_base.cpp:39
msgid ""
"Keeps your saved file and writes the auto-saved version alongside it as a "
"separate timestamped file you can review later."
