msgstr "ຄັງຜັງວົງຈອນ Altium ຫຼື ຄັງແບບລວມສູນ (Integrated Library)"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:89
msgid "File does not appear to be a CADSTAR parts Library file"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ນີ້ເບິ່ງຄືວ່າບໍ່ແມ່ນໄຟລ໌ຄັງອຸປະກອນ CADSTAR"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:133
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Unable to find symbol %s, referenced by part %s. The part was not loaded."
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບສັນຍາລັກ %s ທີ່ອ້າງອີງໂດຍອຸປະກອນ %s. ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:147
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Inconsistent pin numbers in symbol %s compared to the one defined in part "
"%s. The part was not loaded."
msgstr "ເລກຂາໃນສັນຍາລັກ %s ບໍ່ກົງກັບທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນອຸປະກອນ %s. ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:387
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR design contains variants which has no KiCad equivalent. Only the "
"master variant ('%s') was loaded."
msgstr ""
"ການອອກແບບ CADSTAR ນີ້ມີລຸ້ນປ່ຽນ (variants) ທີ່ KiCad ບໍ່ມີສິ່ງທີ່ທຽບເທົ່າ. ຈະໂຫຼດສະເພາະລຸ້ນຫຼັກ "
"('%s') ເທົ່ານັ້ນ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:396
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR design contains grouped items which has no KiCad equivalent. Any "
"grouped items have been ungrouped."
msgstr ""
"ການອອກແບບ CADSTAR ນີ້ມີລາຍການທີ່ຈັດກຸ່ມໄວ້ເຊິ່ງ KiCad ບໍ່ມີສິ່ງທີ່ທຽບເທົ່າ. "
"ລາຍການທີ່ຈັດກຸ່ມທັງໝົດຈະຖືກແຍກກຸ່ມອອກ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:403
#: pcbnew/pcb_io/cadstar/cadstar_pcb_archive_loader.cpp:163
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR design contains re-use blocks which has no KiCad equivalent. The "
"re-use block information has been discarded during the import."
msgstr ""
"ການອອກແບບ CADSTAR ນີ້ມີບລັອກທີ່ນຳໃຊ້ຄືນໃໝ່ (re-use blocks) ເຊິ່ງ KiCad ບໍ່ມີສິ່ງທີ່ທຽບເທົ່າ. "
"ຂໍ້ມູນບລັອກເຫຼົ່ານີ້ຈະຖືກລະເລີຍໃນລະຫວ່າງການນຳເຂົ້າ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:517
msgid ""
"CADSTAR fonts are different to the ones in KiCad. This will likely result in "
"alignment issues. Please review the imported text elements carefully and "
"correct manually if required."
msgstr ""
"ຕົວອັກສອນຂອງ CADSTAR ຕ່າງຈາກຂອງ KiCad. ສິ່ງນີ້ອາດເຮັດໃຫ້ມີບັນຫາໃນການຈັດວາງ. "
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າຢ່າງລະອຽດ ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂດ້ວຍຕົນເອງຖ້າຈຳເປັນ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:522
#: pcbnew/pcb_io/cadstar/cadstar_pcb_archive_loader.cpp:172
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR design has been imported successfully.\n"
"Please review the import errors and warnings (if any)."
msgstr ""
"ນຳເຂົ້າການອອກແບບ CADSTAR ສຳເລັດແລ້ວ.\n"
"ກະລຸນາກວດສອບຂໍ້ຜິດພາດ ແລະ ຄຳເຕືອນໃນການນຳເຂົ້າ (ຖ້າມີ)."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:541
#: pcbnew/pcb_io/cadstar/cadstar_pcb_archive_loader.cpp:76
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The design is too large and cannot be imported into KiCad. \n"
"Please reduce the maximum design size in CADSTAR by navigating to: \n"
"Design Tab -> Properties -> Design Options -> Maximum Design Size. \n"
"Current Design size: %.2f, %.2f millimeters. \n"
"Maximum permitted design size: %.2f, %.2f millimeters.\n"
msgstr ""
"ການອອກແບບນີ້ໃຫຍ່ເກີນໄປ ແລະ ບໍ່ສາມາດນຳເຂົ້າ KiCad ໄດ້. \n"
"ກະລຸນາຫຼຸດຂະໜາດສູງສຸດຂອງການອອກແບບໃນ CADSTAR ໂດຍໄປທີ່: \n"
"Design Tab -> Properties -> Design Options -> Maximum Design Size. \n"
"ຂະໜາດປັດຈຸບັນ: %.2f, %.2f ມິລິແມັດ. \n"
"ຂະໜາດສູງສຸດທີ່ອະນຸຍາດ: %.2f, %.2f ມິລິແມັດ.\n"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:602
msgid ""
"The selected file is a CADSTAR symbol library. It does not contain a "
"schematic design so cannot be imported/opened in this way."
msgstr ""
"ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກແມ່ນຄັງສັນຍາລັກຂອງ CADSTAR. ມັນບໍ່ມີຂໍ້ມູນການອອກແບບຜັງວົງຈອນ ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ສາມາດນຳເຂົ້າ ຫຼື "
"ເປີດດ້ວຍວິທີນີ້ໄດ້."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:607
msgid "The CADSTAR schematic might be corrupt: there is no root sheet."
msgstr "ຜັງວົງຈອນ CADSTAR ອາດຈະເສຍຫາຍ: ບໍ່ພົບແຜ່ນງານຫຼັກ (root sheet)."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:681
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Part definition '%s' references symbol '%s' (alternate '%s') which could not "
"be found in the symbol library. The part has not been loaded into the KiCad "
"library."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳນິຍາມອຸປະກອນ '%s' ອ້າງອີງເຖິງສັນຍາລັກ '%s' (ຕົວສຳຮອງ '%s') ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ພົບໃນຄັງສັນຍາລັກ. "
"ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດເຂົ້າໃນຄັງ KiCad."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:704
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Part definition '%s' has an incomplete definition (no symbol definitions are "
"associated with it). The part has not been loaded into the KiCad library."
msgstr ""
"ຄຳນິຍາມອຸປະກອນ '%s' ບໍ່ຄົບຖ້ວນ (ບໍ່ມີສັນຍາລັກໃດທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ). ອຸປະກອນນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດເຂົ້າໃນຄັງ KiCad."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:751
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol '%s' references part '%s' which could not be found in the library. "
"The symbol was not loaded"
msgstr "ສັນຍາລັກ '%s' ອ້າງອີງເຖິງອຸປະກອນ '%s' ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ພົບໃນຄັງ. ສັນຍາລັກນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດ"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:845
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol ID '%s' references library symbol '%s' which could not be found in "
"the library. Did you export all items of the design?"
msgstr ""
"ລະຫັດສັນຍາລັກ '%s' ອ້າງອີງເຖິງສັນຍາລັກໃນຄັງ '%s' ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ພົບໃນຄັງ. "
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສົ່ງອອກລາຍການທັງໝົດຂອງການອອກແບບແລ້ວບໍ່?"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:857
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol ID '%s' is a signal reference or global signal but it has too many "
"pins. The expected number of pins is 1 but %d were found."
msgstr ""
"ລະຫັດສັນຍາລັກ '%s' ແມ່ນສັນຍານອ້າງອີງ ຫຼື ສັນຍານທົ່ວໄປ ແຕ່ມີຂາຫຼາຍເກີນໄປ. ຄາດວ່າມີ 1 ຂາ ແຕ່ພົບ %d "
"ຂາ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:1000
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol ID '%s' is of an unknown type. It is neither a symbol or a net "
"power / symbol. The symbol was not loaded."
msgstr ""
"ລະຫັດສັນຍາລັກ '%s' ເປັນປະເພດທີ່ບໍ່ຮູ້ຈັກ. ມັນບໍ່ແມ່ນທັງສັນຍາລັກ ຫຼື ສັນຍາລັກໄຟລ້ຽງ. "
"ສັນຍາລັກນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:1016
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol '%s' is scaled in the original CADSTAR schematic but this is not "
"supported in KiCad. When the symbol is reloaded from the library, it will "
"revert to the original 1:1 scale."
msgstr ""
"ສັນຍາລັກ '%s' ຖືກປັບຂະໜາດໃນຜັງວົງຈອນ CADSTAR ຕົ້ນສະບັບ ແຕ່ KiCad ບໍ່ຮອງຮັບສິ່ງນີ້. "
"ເມື່ອມີການໂຫຼດສັນຍາລັກໃໝ່ຈາກຄັງ, ມັນຈະກັບຄືນສູ່ມາດຕາສ່ວນ 1:1 ດັ່ງເດີມ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:1484
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Documentation Symbol '%s' refers to symbol definition ID '%s' which does not "
"exist in the library. The symbol was not loaded."
msgstr ""
"ສັນຍາລັກເອກະສານ '%s' ອ້າງອີງເຖິງລະຫັດຄຳນິຍາມສັນຍາລັກ '%s' ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ມີຢູ່ໃນຄັງ. "
"ສັນຍາລັກນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:1593
msgid "Text Variables could not be set as there is no project attached."
msgstr "ບໍ່ສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຕົວປ່ຽນຂໍ້ຄວາມໄດ້ ເພາະບໍ່ມີໂຄງການທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2120
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol '%s' is rotated by an angle of %.1f degrees in the original CADSTAR "
"design but KiCad only supports rotation angles multiples of 90 degrees. The "
"connecting wires will need manual fixing."
msgstr ""
"ສັນຍາລັກ '%s' ຖືກໝຸນເປັນມຸມ %.1f ອົງສາໃນການອອກແບບ CADSTAR ຕົ້ນສະບັບ ແຕ່ KiCad "
"ຮອງຮັບສະເພາະການໝຸນທີ່ເປັນເທົ່າຕົວຂອງ 90 ອົງສາເທົ່ານັ້ນ. ສາຍໄຟທີ່ເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ຈະຕ້ອງໄດ້ແກ້ໄຂດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2134
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Symbol '%s' references sheet ID '%s' which does not exist in the design. The "
"symbol was not loaded."
msgstr ""
"ສັນຍາລັກ '%s' ອ້າງອີງເຖິງລະຫັດແຜ່ນງານ '%s' ເຊິ່ງບໍ່ມີຢູ່ໃນການອອກແບບ. ສັນຍາລັກນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2270
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Net %s references unknown net element %s. The net was not properly loaded "
"and may require manual fixing."
msgstr ""
"ເນັດ %s ອ້າງອີງເຖິງອົງປະກອບເນັດທີ່ບໍ່ຮູ້ຈັກ %s. ເນັດນີ້ຈຶ່ງຖືກໂຫຼດບໍ່ສົມບູນ ແລະ ອາດຈະຕ້ອງແກ້ໄຂດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2533
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The block ID %s (Block name: '%s') is drawn on sheet '%s' but is not linked "
"to another sheet in the design. KiCad requires all sheet symbols to be "
"associated to a sheet, so the block was not loaded."
msgstr ""
"ລະຫັດບລັອກ %s (ຊື່ບລັອກ: '%s') ຖືກແຕ້ມຢູ່ເທິງແຜ່ນງານ '%s' "
"ແຕ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບແຜ່ນງານອື່ນໃນການອອກແບບ. KiCad "
"ກຳນົດໃຫ້ສັນຍາລັກແຜ່ນງານທັງໝົດຕ້ອງກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບແຜ່ນງານໃດໜຶ່ງ, ບລັອກນີ້ຈຶ່ງບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກໂຫຼດ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/cadstar_sch_archive_loader.cpp:2558
#, c-format
msgid ""
"The CADSTAR schematic might be corrupt: Block %s references a child sheet "
"but has no Figure defined."
msgstr ""
"ຜັງວົງຈອນ CADSTAR ອາດຈະເສຍຫາຍ: ບລັອກ %s ອ້າງອີງເຖິງແຜ່ນງານລູກ ແຕ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຮູບຊົງ (Figure) "
"ໄວ້."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/sch_io_cadstar_archive.cpp:227
msgid ""
"Path to the CADSTAR schematic archive (*.csa) file related to this CADSTAR "
"parts library. If none specified it is assumed to be 'symbol.csa' in the "
"same folder."
msgstr ""
"ເສັ້ນທາງໄປຫາໄຟລ໌ເກັບມ້ຽນຜັງວົງຈອນ CADSTAR (*.csa) ທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບຄັງອຸປະກອນ CADSTAR ນີ້. "
"ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸໄວ້ ຈະຖືວ່າເປັນ 'symbol.csa' ຢູ່ໃນໂຟນເດີດຽວກັນ."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/sch_io_cadstar_archive.cpp:232
msgid ""
"Name of the footprint library related to the symbols in this library. You "
"should create a separate entry for the CADSTAR PCB Archive (*.cpa) file in "
"the footprint library tables. If none specified, 'cadstarpcblib' is assumed."
msgstr ""
"ຊື່ຂອງຄັງຮອຍຕີນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບສັນຍາລັກໃນຄັງນີ້. ທ່ານຄວນສ້າງລາຍການແຍກຕ່າງຫາກສຳລັບໄຟລ໌ CADSTAR PCB "
"Archive (*.cpa) ໃນຕາຕະລາງຄັງຮອຍຕີນ. ຖ້າບໍ່ໄດ້ລະບຸໄວ້ ຈະຖືວ່າເປັນ 'cadstarpcblib'."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/sch_io_cadstar_archive.cpp:279
#, c-format
msgid "Cannot find the .csa file corresponding to library '%s'."
msgstr "ບໍ່ພົບໄຟລ໌ .csa ທີ່ກົງກັບຄັງ '%s'."

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/sch_io_cadstar_archive.h:55
msgid "CADSTAR Schematic Archive files"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ເກັບມ້ຽນຜັງວົງຈອນ CADSTAR"

#: eeschema/sch_io/cadstar/sch_io_cadstar_archive.h:61
msgid "CADSTAR Parts Library files"
msgstr "ໄຟລ໌ຄັງອຸປະກອນ CADSTAR"

