#: kicad/project_tree_pane.cpp:2214
#, c-format
msgid ""
"Push rejected: your local branch and %s have diverged.\n"
"\n"
"This usually happens after amending or rewriting a commit that was already "
"pushed.  Force push to overwrite the remote?\n"
"\n"
"Anyone who already pulled the previous version will need to reset their copy."
msgstr ""
"Push ຖືກປະຕິເສດ: ສາຂາໃນເຄື່ອງ ແລະ %s ມີຄວາມແຕກຕ່າງກັນ.\n"
"\n"
"ສິ່ງນີ້ມັກເກີດຂຶ້ນຫຼັງຈາກມີການ Amend ຫຼື ຂຽນທັບຄອມມິດທີ່ເຄີຍ Push ໄປແລ້ວ. ຕ້ອງການ Force Push "
"ເພື່ອຂຽນທັບ Remote ບໍ່?\n"
"\n"
"ທຸກຄົນທີ່ເຄີຍ Pull ເວີຊັນກ່ອນໜ້າໄປ ຈະຕ້ອງ Reset ຂໍ້ມູນໃນເຄື່ອງໃໝ່."

