#: pcb_calculator/calculator_panels/panel_transline.cpp:59
msgid ""
"'Constant': εr and tan δ applied at all frequencies.\n"
"'Djordjevic-Sarkar': causal wideband Debye anchored at the spec frequency."
msgstr ""
"'ຄົງທີ່': ໃຊ້ εr ແລະ tan δ ໃນທຸກຄວາມຖີ່.\n"
"'Djordjevic-Sarkar': ແບບ Debye ແຖບກວ້າງທີ່ອ້າງອີງຕາມຄວາມຖີ່ສະເພາະ."

#: pcb_calculator/calculator_panels/panel_transline.cpp:65
msgid ""
"Enable solder resist / LPI overlay correction.  Affects εeff, Z0, and "
"dielectric loss for microstrip, coupled microstrip, CPW, and CBCPW."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດການໃຊ້ງານການຊົດເຊີຍຊັ້ນໂຊນເດີມາກ / LPI. ມີຜົນຕໍ່ εeff, Z0 ແລະ dielectric loss ສຳລັບ "
"microstrip, coupled microstrip, CPW ແລະ CBCPW."

#: pcb_calculator/calculator_panels/panel_transline.cpp:69
msgid ""
"Cured mask thickness.  Typical LPI is 15-30 um; set to 0 or uncheck to "
"disable."
msgstr ""
"ຄວາມໜາຂອງມາກທີ່ແຫ້ງແລ້ວ. ປົກກະຕິ LPI ແມ່ນ 15-30 um; ຕັ້ງເປັນ 0 ຫຼື "
"ຍົກເລີກການເລືອກເພື່ອປິດການໃຊ້ງານ."

#: pcb_calculator/calculator_panels/panel_transline.cpp:74
msgid ""
"Mask relative permittivity.  Default 3.5 for standard green LPI.  Range "
"3.3-3.8 for typical resins."
msgstr ""
"ຄ່າຄວາມຊຶມຊາບໄດອີເລັກທຣິກຂອງມາກ. ຄ່າມາດຕະຖານ 3.5 ສຳລັບ LPI ສີຂຽວມາດຕະຖານ. ຊ່ວງ "
"3.3-3.8 ສຳລັບເຣຊິນທົ່ວໄປ."

#: pcb_calculator/calculator_panels/panel_transline.cpp:79
msgid "Mask loss tangent.  Default 0.025 for LPI."
msgstr "ຄ່າ Loss tangent ຂອງມາກ. ຄ່າມາດຕະຖານ 0.025 ສຳລັບ LPI."

#: pcb_calculator/calculator_panels/panel_transline.cpp:83
msgid ""
"Enable when the mask fills the CPW slots (standard LPI process).\n"
"Disable for selective mask that covers only the traces."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ເມື່ອມາກເຕັມຊ່ອງຫວ່າງ CPW (ຂະບວນການ LPI ມາດຕະຖານ).\n"
"ປິດໃຊ້ສຳລັບມາກທີ່ເຄືອບສະເພາະແຕ່ເສັ້ນລາຍໄຟ."

