#: pcbnew/dialogs/dialog_pad_properties_base.cpp:619
msgid ""
"Optional property to specify a special purpose or constraint in fabrication "
"files:\n"
"BGA attribute is for pads in BGA footprints\n"
"Fiducial local is a fiducial for the parent footprint\n"
"Fiducial global is a fiducial for the whole board\n"
"Test Point specifies an electrical test point\n"
"Heatsink specifies a thermal pad\n"
"Castellated specifies a through hole pad on a board edge\n"
"Mechanical specifies a through-hole pad that is used for mechanical support"
msgstr ""
"ຄຸນສົມບັດທາງເລືອກເພື່ອລະບຸຈຸດປະສົງພິເສດ ຫຼື ຂໍ້ຈຳກັດໃນໄຟລ໌ການຜະລິດ:\n"
"BGA attribute ແມ່ນສຳລັບ pads ໃນ BGA footprints\n"
"Fiducial local ແມ່ນ fiducial ສຳລັບ footprint ແມ່\n"
"Fiducial global ແມ່ນ fiducial ສຳລັບທັງແຜ່ນວົງຈອນ\n"
"Test Point ລະບຸຈຸດທົດສອບທາງໄຟຟ້າ\n"
"Heatsink ລະບຸແຜ່ນຮອງລະບາຍຄວາມຮ້ອນ\n"
"Castellated ລະບຸ pad ແບບ through hole ທີ່ຂອບແຜ່ນວົງຈອນ\n"
"Mechanical ລະບຸ pad ແບບ through hole ທີ່ໃຊ້ເພື່ອການຮອງຮັບທາງກົນຈັກ"

