#: pcbnew/exporters/step/exporter_step.cpp:1441
msgid ""
"This error may indicate insufficient memory. Consider disabling 'Fuse "
"Shapes', reducing the number of vias/components, or freeing system memory.\n"
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດນີ້ອາດໝາຍເຖິງໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳບໍ່ພຽງພໍ. ລອງປິດ 'Fuse Shapes', ຫຼຸດຈຳນວນເວຍ/ອຸປະກອນ, ຫຼື "
"ຄືນພື້ນທີ່ໜ່ວຍຄວາມຈຳລະບົບ.\n"

#: pcbnew/exporters/step/exporter_step.cpp:1447
#, c-format
